data.description: Don't miss out on this amazing home in the heart of Kern, 2 blocks from Madeline Park! From the inviting front porch to the bright & open floor plan, this home is great for every day living & entertaining! Beautifully remodeled w/ refinished hardwood floors thru-out and loaded w/ charm! Attractive open concept kitchen features quartz counter tops, SS appliances and a spacious pantry. Primary bedroom w/ exquisitely remodeled ensuite bath w/ heated floors and custom walk-in closet. 2 additional flex spaces can be used as an office, workout room, additional living room. Numerous updates including HVAC. BONUS GUEST HOUSE, perfect for additional living area or in-law quarters (included in sq ft). Enjoy the beautiful back deck & yard as summer winds down & year around! Walking distance to area restaurants, grocery store, 2 pharmacies, UTEP, Billy Rogers Arroyo Park, Palisades Canyon hiking trail, El Paso Tennis Club & Swimming Club! Washer, Dryer & Refrigerator included. Super long driveway leading to 1 car garage
